<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" dir="ltr">

<head>
  <%- include("./partials/head.ejs")%>

</head>

<body>
  <%- include("./partials/navbar.ejs") %>

  <main>

    <div id="myCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel">
      <div class="carousel-indicators">
        <button type="button" data-bs-target="#myCarousel" data-bs-slide-to="0" class="active" aria-current="true" aria-label="Slide 1"></button>
        <button type="button" data-bs-target="#myCarousel" data-bs-slide-to="1" aria-label="Slide 2"></button>
        <button type="button" data-bs-target="#myCarousel" data-bs-slide-to="2" aria-label="Slide 3"></button>
      </div>
      <div class="carousel-inner">
        <div class="carousel-item active">
          <svg class="bd-placeholder-img" width="100%" height="100%" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice" focusable="false">
            <rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="#5584AC" />
          </svg>

          <div class="container">
            <div class="carousel-caption text-start">
              <h1>Welcome to MediHelp!</h1>
              <p>This website is dedicated to helping its users better understand and manage their medicines</p>

            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
          <svg class="bd-placeholder-img" width="100%" height="100%" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice" focusable="false">
            <rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="#5584AC" />
          </svg>

          <div class="container">
            <div class="carousel-caption">
              <h1>Empowering yourself with knowledge</h1>
              <p>Use our services to look up your latest prescriptions and see just exactly they are! We also offer a notification service and database to keep track of all your medicines.</p>

            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
          <svg class="bd-placeholder-img" width="100%" height="100%" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice" focusable="false">
            <rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="#5584AC" />
          </svg>

          <div class="container">
            <div class="carousel-caption text-end">
              <h1>What are you waiting for?</h1>
              <p>Sign up today for free. And unlike other services, this website is not monetized so we won't sell your info to other companies or spam you with ads. Its entirely free!</p>
              <p><a class="btn btn-lg btn-primary" href="/sign-up">Sign-up!</a></p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#myCarousel" data-bs-slide="prev">
        <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
      </button>
      <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#myCarousel" data-bs-slide="next">
        <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
      </button>
    </div>


    <!-- Marketing messaging and featurettes. Adding the menu.ejs for presenting several options or details
    ================================================== -->
    <!-- Wrap the rest of the page in another container to center all the content. -->

    <%- include("./partials/Menu.ejs") %>


    <!-- START THE FEATURETTES -->

    <hr class="featurette-divider">

    <div class="row featurette">
      <div class="col-md-7">
        <h2 class="featurette-heading">MediSearch, <span> helping you to find out more.</span></h2>
        <p class="lead">MediSearch is service to look up and find out more about your prescrition. It does this by implementing the puppeteer library and scraping the web for info on what every you typed in</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-5">
        <img src="/images/big-search.png" alt="big searching image">
      </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="featurette-divider">

    <div class="row featurette">
      <div class="col-md-7 order-md-2">
        <h2 class="featurette-heading">MediBase <span>keeps track of your meidcation for you.</span></h2>
        <p class="lead">Keep strack of your medication by storing in MediBase where you will be able to access list of medications and information on the from anywhere in the world as long as you have an internet connection</p>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-5 order-md-1">
        <img src="/images/database.png" alt="database image">
      </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="featurette-divider">

    <div class="row featurette">
      <div class="col-md-7">
        <h2 class="featurette-heading">MediNotice, <span>the service that will never let you forget your medications ever again.</span></h2>
        <p class="lead">Service is currently unavailable. Will be implemented using the twilio api at a later date.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-5">
        <img src="/images/big-notification.png" alt="big-notification image">
      </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="featurette-divider">

    <!-- /END THE FEATURETTES -->

    </div><!-- /.container -->


    <!-- FOOTER -->
    <%- include("./partials/footer.ejs")%>
  </main>
</body>

</html>
